Joichi Ito is a very influential 'digerati', venture capitalist and supporter of the Commons.


=Webcast 1=

This is a documentary, in Japanese and English but with English subtitles throughout, that present his thoughts on a variety of subjects, mostly the importance of games like World of Warcraft, but also the Creative Commons and other topics.

Contains also promotional material on the many projects in which Joi Ito has invested, such as Technorati. 50 minutes long.

URL = http://www.dotsub.com/films/jicc/index.php


=Webcast 2=

Joi Ito interviewed by Loic Lemeur at Aula 2006

URL = http://www.loiclemeur.com/english/2006/06/joi_ito_a_podca.html

Also available in podcast only format.


